cultural.title: Dance
cultural.description: Dance, the movement of the body in a rhythmic way, usually to music and within a given space, for the purpose of expressing an idea or emotion, releasing energy, or simply taking delight in the movement itself.

cultural.title: Singing
cultural.description: Singers read and interpret musical compositions and apply their voice and style to create a song.

cultural.title: Art
cultural.description: Art is a diverse range of human activities in creating intended to be appreciated for their beauty or emotional power.

cultural.title: Drama
cultural.description: Drama is a composition in verse or prose presenting a story in pantomime or dialogue.
